{"tid":1015374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]印度發生飲假酒中毒事件 至今90人死亡","createTime":"2019-02-10T02:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T04:44:12.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a31a7a93d84612376f193b8fa77b2c13d5fe8ba6","tid":1015374,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cms.exmoo.com/uploads/2019-02-10/S5yUwtxlkMxLO15uRZto.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2019-02-10%2FS5yUwtxlkMxLO15uRZto.jpg&h=516cfad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度北方邦及北阿坎德邦近日發生的假酒中毒事件，造成的死亡人數據報已增至近90人，另有多人仍在醫院治療。據《今日印度》周刊報道，在北方邦的薩哈蘭普爾地區和北阿坎德邦的魯爾基地區，分別有46人和20人死亡。此外，在這兩個邦的其他地區還有約20人死亡。但上述死亡人數尚未得到印度官方確認。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，當局在事發後大力打擊製造假酒活動，拘捕至少8名假酒販售商，查獲超過400升的假酒，另外23名涉案官員及12名警察被停職調查。另一方面，北方邦政府宣布，將向每名死者家屬及不適的人分別發放 20 萬及 5萬盧比慰問金。<br />\n<br />\n印度合法酒價高昂，平民難以負擔，故有不法商人兜售混入工業酒精的假酒，令假酒中毒事件時有發生。雖然印度政府三令五申禁止銷售假酒，但管控不嚴。"},{"pid":"224c0bfc2d53cba1234fc490f8206c49d091fd41","tid":1015374,"uid":838,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"大陸有一個農夫，花了畢生所有積蓄，買了一包種子，播在田地裡，<br />\n但是，到了秋天卻依無所獲。<br />\n因為---------種子是假的......<br />\n老農夫決心一死，便買了一灌農藥喝下，結果沒死。<br />\n因為---------農藥是假的......<br />\n由於人沒有死，一家人都很慶幸。<br />\n便買了一瓶好酒全家一起喝，結果全家人都死了........<br />\n因為---------酒也是假的......<br />\n哈哈~~都是假的!!假酒~~喝了就死了!!"},{"pid":"a331c7d71010770a8646855a2a4a6cce526f7b92","tid":1015374,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:25:09.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1049af599c4fde1421ab650c80d20c93ebe17d16","tid":1015374,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"死九十個 生返九千個 冇所謂喇"},{"pid":"afaf38a036578dae9ade96441505f4e7760254ee","tid":1015374,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"@慘過返印度"},{"pid":"c5cd18aefe2a7bf19a02eae4eb16e7d4b76f55dc","tid":1015374,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79e6ff777aa66f8b6d9b37886cc914359745eb5","tid":1015374,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/a4/1xh6.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140126135451\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Fa4%2F1xh6.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140126135451&h=226d9250&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0b3ec1b1a1236abda45115c88cd10aa7049e95a","tid":1015374,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T04:30:13.000Z","msg":"估錯國家"},{"pid":"74936caac92cb66486470174cf5f589a9f5ce895","tid":1015374,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}